CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 7, 1959, pg. 2, reads: "DBR Casts His Vote - Prothonotary David B. Roberts is shown casting his vote last Tuesday in Fifth Ward's 17th District polling place at A. Leo Weil School. Mr. Roberts, Democratic committeeman in the district, topped all candidates in the ward, while Councilman Paul F. Jones was right behind him.  Election officials, shown are William H. Berry, Mrs. Alberta Jackson, Anna M. Green and Lewis C. Johnson."
TitMainTitle: David B. Roberts signing card in polling place, with William H. Berry, Alberta Jackson, Anna M. Green, and Lewis C. Johnson on opposite side of table, at A. Leo Weil School
